l add a new button to the editor, where a file manager can be opened to manage files and insert them into the content area.</p>\r<p>Learn more about the <a title=\"WP Edit Pro File Manager\" href=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/wpeditpro/~learn.wpeditpro.com/wp-edit-pro-file-manager/\" target=\"_blank\">WP Edit Pro File Manager</a>.</p>\r<div class = \"alert alert-info \">WP Edit Pro Bonus Page\r<br>\r<a href=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/wpeditpro/~wpeditpro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/bonus_page.png\"><img src=\"http://wpeditpro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/bonus_page.png\" alt=\"bonus_page\" width=\"1339\" height=\"552\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1114\" /></a></div>\r<h3>Advanced Insert/Edit Image Button</h3>\r<p>As requested on the support forum, size controls have been added to the Advanced Insert/Edit Image button. This works much like Photoshop, or any other photo editor software. If the option is selected to maintain image proportions; as the height or width is adjusted, the opposing size will auto-adjust.</p>\r<div class = \"alert alert-info \">Advanced Insert/Edit Image Size Proportions\r<br>\r<a href=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/wpeditpro/~wpeditpro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/adv_image.png\"><img src=\"http://wpeditpro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/adv_image.png\" alt=\"adv_image\" width=\"1154\" height=\"609\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1117\" /></a></div>\r<h3>Advanced Insert/Edit Link</h3>\r<p>The advanced link button also has a couple of new features.  The ability to search through existing WordPress posts/pages/custom post types has been added.</p>\r<div class = \"alert alert-info \">Advanced Insert/Edit Link Search Capability\r<br>\r<a href=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/wpeditpro/~wpeditpro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/adv_link.png\"><img src=\"http://wpeditpro.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/adv_link.png\" alt=\"adv_link\" width=\"585\" height=\"473\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1118\" /></a></div>\r<h2>WP Edit Pro HTTPS Upgrade</h2>\r<p>We recently updated our website to the https protocol.  This will help ensure data is protected/encrypted when being sent from our server.</p>\r<p>This upgrade required we update the links in both the plugin; and the activation scripts on our server.  Previous versions of the plugin will continue to activate properly; but the update notifications will not come through to the admin panel.</p>\r<p>Installing and activating version 1.9 will ensure the update process is put into place correctly.</p>\r<p>We will be releasing version 1.9.1 very soon.  This release will only serve as verification that the automatic update process is working properly.</p>\r<Img align=\"left\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:0;float:left;margin:0;padding:0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/i/81974113/0/wpeditpro\">\r\n\n<div style=\"clear:both;padding-top:0.2em;\"><a title=\"Like on Facebook\" href=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/28/81974113/wpeditpro\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"http://assets.feedblitz.com/i/fblike20.png\" style=\"border:0;margin:0;padding:0;\"></a>&#160;<a title=\"Share on Google+\" href=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/30/81974113/wpeditpro\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"http://assets.feedblitz.com/i/googleplus20.png\" style=\"border:0;margin:0;padding:0;\"></a>&#160;<a title=\"Pin it!\" href=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/29/81974113/wpeditpro,http%3a%2f%2fwpeditpro.com%2fwp-content%2fuploads%2f2014%2f07%2fbonus_page.png\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"http://assets.feedblitz.com/i/pinterest20.png\" style=\"border:0;margin:0;padding:0;\"></a>&#160;<a title=\"Tweet This\" href=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/24/81974113/wpeditpro\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"http://assets.feedblitz.com/i/twitter20.png\" style=\"border:0;margin:0;padding:0;\"></a>&#160;<a title=\"Subscribe by email\" href=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/19/81974113/wpeditpro\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"http://assets.feedbl